Hello for Video Ads on your platform whats the dimensions etc

Hi there! For video ads on NewsBreak, we recommend using the following dimensions and specifications: 
- Aspect Ratio: 16:9 
- Resolution: At least 720p (1280x720) 
- File Format: MP4 or MOV 
- Maximum File Size: 1GB. 
For more detailed information, you can check out our guide here: [Account Management Guide](https://help.newsbreak.com/hc/en-us/articles/17539290349709-Account-Management-Guide).
